reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Over all pleased
reviews.reviewText: Super happy with this purchase. Will work perfectly in the space needed. Buying to replace plastic drawers and this has way more room and seems less clumsy overall.Matches bedroom furniture and takes up a small footprint while offering lots of storage.Super easy to put together once you get the first connecting bottom bar in. Took less than 20 mins total. There’s no bad smell and instructions are clear. The box came with a ribbon taped to outside to assist in opening the box and that was a nice touch. I also like that the feet are adjustable to make it balanced evenly on uneven floors.Put two more in my cart for various small space areas in my home. We will see how the drawers hold up, but they seem decently sturdy.Only negative and it’s not even a bad remark is the color is Al more of a beige than a light gray. Not that awful as it’s still aesthetically pleasing, but I did notice the color was a bit darker than anticipated. Phone screen brightness or whatever, it’s fine! Super happy and will update if quality doesn’t hold up.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice little dresser
reviews.reviewText: I bought this to furnish our guest bedroom. I was pleasantly surprised at how nice it looks when assembled. It looks just like the photo in the advertisement. It was easy to put together in about 15 minutes. It is not something I would use to store something very heavy, but is perfect for clothing or other belongings brought by guests. I also liked that it was the perfect size for our room and a reasonable price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This little dresser is just perfect for my needs! I put it in my closet with my winter clothes in it and I'll swap for my summer clothes in a month or so.So much easier than putting them in the spare bedroom closet like I*'ve done for years! It was easy to pout together--took me less than an hour! It's sturdy enough that I don't worry about putting things on top of it. It's also light enough that I can move it myself--and I'm 66 years old with NUMEROUS medical issues including 3 herniated disks in my back. I would definitely buy it again and recommend it to friends/family who need a little extra storage space.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good lil purchase
reviews.reviewText: Super easy to put together, not extremely heavy, but heavy enough to be sturdy. It came with all the parts, no scratched pieces, and a mini screw driver.Although it’s a bit on the smaller side, it matches the dimensions and is exactly what I needed for my sons room. Maybe I’m a little concerned about the durability but I got this for like 45 bucks. You can’t put too much heavy items in the drawers or it’ll definitely affect the shape of the drawers- because they are foldable cube drawers that are a softer material. It also comes with items to attach to the wall if you need that extra layer of sturdiness. All in all I’m happy with my purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for my daughter to put my grandsons clothes in. She loves it!! It’s so easy to assemble and it looks really nice! It holds a lot and is lightweight. I would definitely recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 2, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The only thing I wish I did differently is buy more of these! I only purchased 1 of these and I regret not purchasing more for my closet. This drawer is way sturdier than I thought it would be, and holds a good amount of clothing items.It was easy to assemble (1 person), easy to move around, and because of that, it's easy to clean underneath and around. It does smell bad at first, I'm assuming it's the plastic smell - but it does go away in time. That was something I was extremely worried about initially but now it's so much better!
